    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's not just a temporary slump though. it feels permanent. like the version of me that actually mattered is dead, and i'm just the ghost left behind. and honestly, even the idea of \"small activities\" feels exhausting. why bother trying to refill a well that's just... dry? it feels like i'm just pretending to exist at this point.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
